# Binary assets: never let core.autocrlf touch these. Without this,
# git's binary-detection heuristic can misfire on a later checkout/add
# and silently corrupt the file by converting line endings inside
# binary data. Confirmed happening for real in the sibling planning repo.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.mp4 binary
*.mov binary
*.webm binary
*.zip binary
*.exe binary
*.ico binary
